sequenceDiagram
    participant Eng as Security Engineer
    participant CLI as norviq redteam
    participant Sim as AttackSimulator
    participant API as Norviq API
    participant Eval as /api/v1/evaluate
    participant Rep as RedTeamReporter
    Eng->>CLI: run --agent customer-support
    CLI->>Sim: run_suite()
    loop each attack
        Sim->>API: POST /api/v1/evaluate
        API->>Eval: policy decision
        Eval-->>Sim: decision + rule_id
    end
    Sim-->>CLI: SuiteReport
    CLI->>Rep: to_json/to_markdown
    Rep-->>Eng: report output
